title: Men's Tennis Falls to Tennessee Tech 4-3 on Thursday Afternoon - University of Tennessee at Chattanooga Athletics - GoMocs.com
content: Men's Tennis Falls to Tennessee Tech 4-3 on Thursday Afternoon - University of Tennessee at Chattanooga Athletics  GoMocs.com
description: COOKEVILLE, Tenn. --- The Chattanooga Mocs men's tennis team suffered a tight and hard-fought 4-3 loss to in-state foe Tennessee Tech in non-conference action in Cookeville, Tennessee on Thursday afternoon.
